import React, { Component } from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'

// Components
import FullScreen from '../fullscreen'
import Topic from '../topic'
import Box from './box'

const Container = styled.div`
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(minmax(2, auto-fit), minmax(200px, 1fr));
  grid-auto-flow: dense;
  grid-gap: 20px;
`

class Activity extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <FullScreen>
        <Topic>Activities</Topic>
        <Container>
          <Box>1</Box>
          <Box>2</Box>
          <Box>3</Box>
          <Box>4</Box>
          <Box>5</Box>
          <Box>6</Box>
          <Box>7</Box>
          <Box>8</Box>
          <Box>9</Box>
          <Box>10</Box>
          <Box>11</Box>
          <Box>12</Box>
          <Box>13</Box>
          <Box>14</Box>
          <Box>14</Box>
          <Box>14</Box>
          <Box>14</Box>
          <Box>14</Box>
          <Box>14</Box>
          <Box>14</Box>
          <Box>14</Box>
          <Box>14</Box>
          <Box>14</Box>
          <Box>14</Box>
        </Container>
      </FullScreen>
    )
  }
}

export default Activity
